languages.text: "Д-дом Орселлио всегда был верен новатору Тисифоне. И отныне — верен ее наследнице, пусть даже вы поведете нас иным путем, моя госпожа!" {n}Голос Леди-Навигатора благоговейно дрожит.{/n}

languages.text: "House Orsellio was always loyal to Novator Tisiphone. Henceforth, it will be loyal to her successor, even if you see fit to lead us down a different path, my lady!" {n}The Navigator's voice trembles with reverence.{/n}

languages.text: 「オーセリオ家はずっとノベイター・ティシフォンに忠誠を誓っていました。ただ今より、その後継者に忠誠を誓いましょう、これまでの道を外れるとしても。閣下！」{n}航宙士の声は畏敬の念で震えている。{/n}
languages.original_text: "House Orsellio was always loyal to Novator Tisiphone. Henceforth, it will be loyal to her successor, even if you see fit to lead us down a different path, my lady!" {n}The Navigator's voice trembles with reverence.{/n}

traits.locale_text: 「オーセリオ家はずっとノベイター・ティシフォンに忠誠を誓っていました。ただ今より、その後継者に忠誠を誓いましょう、これまでの道を外れるとしても。閣下！」{n}航宙士の声は畏敬の念で震えている。{/n}
traits.speaker: CW_NaviTraditionalistLeader

languages.text: “奥赛罗家族始终忠于提西福涅，从今往后也会忠于她的继承人。哪怕您认为我们应当踏上另一条道路，我们也愿意追随您，我的女士！”{n}导航者的声音颤抖着，充满了崇敬的意味。{/n}
languages.original_text: "House Orsellio was always loyal to Novator Tisiphone. Henceforth, it will be loyal to her successor, even if you see fit to lead us down a different path, my lady!" {n}The Navigator's voice trembles with reverence.{/n}

traits.locale_text: “奥塞罗家族始终忠于提西福涅，从今往后也会忠于她的继承人。哪怕您认为我们应当踏上另一条道路，我们也愿意追随您，我的女士！”{n}导航者的声音颤抖着，充满了崇敬的意味。{/n}
traits.speaker: CW_NaviTraditionalistLeader

languages.text: « La maison Orsellio... s'est toujours montrée loyale envers la Novator Tisiphone. Je serai donc loyale à son héritière, et ce, même si vous décidez de nous mener sur une autre voie, ma dame ! » {n}La voix du navigateur tremble tant il ne peut contenir sa vénération.{/n}
languages.original_text: "House Orsellio was always loyal to Novator Tisiphone. Henceforth, it will be loyal to her successor, even if you see fit to lead us down a different path, my lady!" {n}The Navigator's voice trembles with reverence.{/n}

traits.speaker: CW_NaviTraditionalistLeader

languages.text: «La casa Orsellio siempre ha sido leal a la Novator Tisiphone. ¡De ahora en adelante, será leal a su sucesora, aunque nos conduzca por otro camino, mi señora!». {n}La voz del Navegante tiembla con veneración.{/n}
languages.original_text: "House Orsellio was always loyal to Novator Tisiphone. Henceforth, it will be loyal to her successor, even if you see fit to lead us down a different path, my lady!" {n}The Navigator's voice trembles with reverence.{/n}

traits.speaker: CW_NaviTraditionalistLeader

languages.text: "Das Haus Orsellio war Novatorin Tisiphone immer treu ergeben. Fortan wird es deren Nachfolgerin treu ergeben sein, selbst wenn Ihr entscheidet, uns auf einen anderen Pfad zu führen, Mylady!" {n}Die Stimme der Navigatorin bebt vor Ehrfurcht.{/n}
languages.original_text: "House Orsellio was always loyal to Novator Tisiphone. Henceforth, it will be loyal to her successor, even if you see fit to lead us down a different path, my lady!" {n}The Navigator's voice trembles with reverence.{/n}

languages.text: "Orsellio Hanesi, daima Rota Reisi Tisiphone'ye sadakatini göstermiştir. Onun halefi sizsiniz, farklı bir yoldan yürümemizi uygun görürseniz dahi size sadakat göstereceğiz leydim!" {n}Rotacı'nın sesi, hürmetle titriyor.{/n}

traits.locale_text: "Orsellio Hanesi, daima Rota Reisi Tisiphone'ye sadakatini göstermiştir. Bizim için farklı bir yolu uygun görseniz bile artık onun halefi olarak size sadakatimizi göstereceğiz leydim!" {n}Rotacının sesi, hürmetle titriyor.{/n}
traits.speaker: CW_NaviTraditionalistLeader
